import { View, Text,ImageBackground,TouchableOpacity,Image} from 'react-native'
import React from 'react'

const ScreenPlayGame = () => {
  return (
    <View>
      <ImageBackground source={require('../assets/bc2.png')} style={{width:'100%',height:'100%'}}></ImageBackground>
      <View style={styles.longcho}>
      <TouchableOpacity>
          <Image source={require('../assets/1.png')} style={{width:60,height:60,}} />
        </TouchableOpacity>
      </View>
      <View>
      <TouchableOpacity>
          <Image source={require('../assets/2.png')} style={{width:60,height:60,}} />
        </TouchableOpacity>
      </View>

       </View>
    
  )
}
const styles = StyleSheet.create({
  longcho:{
    flex:1,
    marginLeft:230,
    marginTop:50,
    flexDirection:'row',
    width:20,
    height:20,
    
  }

})


export default ScreenPlayGame
